Question on Notes command
-----------------------------
1) How would you compress a directory named project into a bzip2-compressed tar archive called project.tar.bz2?

2) How would you compress a directory named logs into a .zip file called logs.zip using a single command?

3) How would you extract the contents of the gzip-compressed tar archive mydir.tar.gz into the current directory?

4) Write a command that compresses a directory named mydir into a gzip-compressed archive called mydir.tar.gz.

